OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,FThe sister of a headteacher who took
OL,7,Fher own life has joined calls for the
OL,8,FGovernment to delay proposed changes
OL,9,Fto Ofsted school inspections.
OL,11,FRuth Perry took her own life in
OL,12,FJanuary 2023 after an Ofsted report
OL,13,Fdowngraded her Caversham Primary
OL,14,FSchool in Reading to the lowest
OL,15,Foverall effectiveness rating over
OL,16,Fsafeguarding concerns.
