OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,FIn an open letter to Education
OL,7,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson released
OL,8,Fon Monday, her sister Professor Julia
OL,9,FWaters joined school leaders, national
OL,10,Forganisations and former inspectors
OL,11,Fwho said there were "real concerns"
OL,12,Fthe proposals could drive "excessive
OL,13,Fpressure, ill-health and stress for
OL,14,Fthe profession" for education
OL,15,Fprofessionals.
OL,17,F"We believe the proposed new system
OL,18,Fwill continue to have a detrimental
OL,19,Fimpact on the wellbeing of education
OL,20,Fstaff and hence on students' school
OL,21,Fexperience," the letter read.
