OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,F"In particular, we believe the
OL,7,Fproposed new report cards and the new
OL,8,Fgrading system fail to address the
OL,9,Frecommendations of the coroner
OL,10,Ffollowing the tragic, preventable
OL,11,Fdeath of Ruth Perry.
OL,13,F"They also fail to address the
OL,14,Frecommendations of the Education
OL,15,FSelect Committee's inquiry into the
OL,16,Fwork of Ofsted, which was launched as
OL,17,Fa result of wider concerns highlighted
OL,18,Fby Ruth's terrible death."
