OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,FA Department for Education spokeswoman
OL,7,Fsaid reforms play a "central" role in
OL,8,Fwork to raise school standards.
OL,10,F"The system this Government inherited
OL,11,Fwas high stakes for teachers but low
OL,12,Finformation for parents, which is why
OL,13,Fwe're removing single-word judgment
OL,14,Fand introducing school report cards,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
