OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,F"Both Ofsted's and the department's
OL,7,Fconsultations have provided an
OL,8,Fimportant opportunity for everyone to
OL,9,Fhave their say and both organisations
OL,10,Fwill carefully consider all responses
OL,11,Fbefore finalising the approach."
OL,13,FA motion passed at the National
OL,14,FEducation Union (NEU) conference in
OL,15,FHarrogate earlier this month called on
OL,16,Fthe union's executive to renew its
OL,17,Fcampaign to "expose the harm, damage
OL,18,Fand cover-up" from the watchdog, and
OL,19,Fto instead call for an "effective and
OL,20,Ffair" school improvement system with
OL,21,Fno "ranking and shaming".
