OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,FIt added that members who "take action
OL,7,Fto protect themselves to keep safe
OL,8,Fwhere they have evidence that Ofsted
OL,9,Fis placing them in serious and
OL,10,Fimminent danger of harm or death"
OL,11,Fshould be supported.
OL,13,FThe Government announced last year
OL,14,Fthat headline Ofsted grades for
OL,15,Foverall effectiveness for schools in
OL,16,FEngland would be scrapped.
OL,18,FPreviously, Ofsted awarded one of four
OL,19,Fsingle-phrase inspection judgments:
OL,20,Foutstanding, good, requires
OL,21,Fimprovement and inadequate.
