OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,FThe move came after Ofsted faced
OL,7,Fcriticism following Ms Perry's death.
OL,9,FIn February, Ofsted launched a
OL,10,Fconsultation on its plans to introduce
OL,11,Fa report card system for grading
OL,12,Fschools in England.
OL,14,FSchools could be graded across eight
OL,15,Fto 10 areas of a provision, including
OL,16,Fattendance, inclusion and behaviour,
OL,17,Fusing a colour-coded five-point scale.
