OL,3,CRuth Perry's sister joins calls to
OL,4,Chalt proposed Ofsted reforms
OL,6,FThey would receive ratings, from the
OL,7,Fred-coloured "causing concern" to
OL,8,Forange-coloured "attention needed",
OL,9,Fthrough the green shades of "secure",
OL,10,F"strong" and "exemplary" for each area
OL,11,Fof practice.
OL,13,FA survey of more than 12,000 NEU
OL,14,Fteacher members in English state
OL,15,Fschools, released at the union's
OL,16,Fannual conference, suggests the
OL,17,Fmajority (57%) feel inspection
OL,18,Fnegatively affects their mental health.
